 contrast with the conventional $B-L$ extension\nof the SM or MSSM where the right-handed neutrinos are heavy Majorana particles\nand decay to the SM leptons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Mar 2016 00:00:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-08"}
