ot case with an approximation ratio of $\\tfrac{1}{2}\\cos\n\\frac{\\phi}{2}$ and a running time complexity of only ${O}(N\\log N)$, $N$\nstanding for the aggregate number of user demands, which can be implemented\nefficiently in practice.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Mar 2016 03:56:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2016 13:21:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 10 Oct 2018 02:46:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-06"}
